cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.NE, cs.DC, cs.SY

The paper focuses on mobile deep learning for personal mobile sensing applications, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed framework also involves multi-agent reinforcement learning (cs.MA) to balance resources and synchronous stochastic gradient descent (cs.NE) to reduce overhead. The resource constraint and failure by attacks mentioned in the abstract suggest a potential connection to distributed computing (cs.DC) and system and control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
